post.description:
Upgrade PowerFlex Manager VM to a newer version.

Here is a sample CURL command with a payload: 

curl -k --request POST https://$IN_IP/Api/V1/Appliance/upgrade --header 'Content-Type: application/json' --header "Authorization: Bearer $PM_TOKEN" --data '
{
    "location": "https://amaas-eos-drm1.cec.lab.emc.com/artifactory/vxfm-yum-release/pfmp20/PFMP2-4.5.0-xxx.tgz",
    "nodes": {
        "nodes": [
            {
                "credential": {
                    "password": "admin",
                    "type": "password"
                },
                "name": "node1",
                "ipAddress": "100.68.101.101",
                "username": "root"
            },
            {
                "credential": {
                    "password": "admin",
                    "type": "password"
                },
                "name": "node2",
                "ipAddress": "100.68.101.92",
                "username": "root"
            },
            {
                "credential": {
                    "password": "admin",
                    "type": "password"
                },
                "name": "node3",
                "ipAddress": "100.68.101.93",
                "username": "root"
            }
        ]
    },
    "password": "",
    "username": ""
}'
